    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it really seems like the \"innovation\" argument is just something used to justify these mandates. if the benefits are mostly speculative and the costs are immediate and guaranteed, does it even make sense to call this a balanced policy? it feels more like a way to push small players out of the market in favor of big corps who can afford it.",
